Subject: Cannot access the URL and lost root password
Description: Upon login it shows disk is full.
Solution_Comment__c:
- cleared locations on the system disk related to email alerts
- cleared the database of the unsent email alerts
- reset the root UI login password
- advised to either delete Alerts or configure the System Configuration -> System Settings -> Email SMTP settings as this not being configured caused the issue
- reset the uninstall password for agents.
